FAQ_Q_18=Does Diamond support Phobos?
FAQ_A_18:
  Yes. All functionality of Phobos is theoretically available and can be used in Diamond.<br>
  <br>
  Some functionality is available implicit in views such as certain functions from std.conv, std.algorithm, std.array, std.string etc.
;

